001package edu.cnm.deepdive.teamle.model.entity;
002
003import androidx.annotation.NonNull;
004import androidx.room.ColumnInfo;
005import androidx.room.Entity;
006import androidx.room.ForeignKey;
007import androidx.room.Index;
008import androidx.room.PrimaryKey;
009import java.time.Duration;
010import java.time.Instant;
011
012  @Entity(
013      tableName = "game_result",
014      indices = @Index(value = {"guess_count", "duration"}),
015      foreignKeys = @ForeignKey(entity = User.class, parentColumns = "user_id", childColumns = "user_id",
016          onDelete = ForeignKey.CASCADE)
017  )
018
019  public class GameResult {
020
021    @PrimaryKey(autoGenerate = true)
022    @ColumnInfo(name = "game_result_id")
023    private long id;
024
025    @NonNull
026    @ColumnInfo(index = true)
027    private Instant timestamp = Instant.now();
028
029    @ColumnInfo(name = "size", index = true)
030    private int size;
031
032    @ColumnInfo(name = "guess_count", index = true)
033    private int guessCount;
034
035    @NonNull
036    @ColumnInfo(index = true)
037    private Duration duration = Duration.ZERO;
038
039    @ColumnInfo(name = "user_id", index = true)
040    private Long userId;
041
042    public long getId() {
043      return id;
044    }
045
046    public void setId(long id) {
047      this.id = id;
048    }
049
050    @NonNull
051    public Instant getTimestamp() {
052      return timestamp;
053    }
054
055    public void setTimestamp(@NonNull Instant timestamp) {
056      this.timestamp = timestamp;
057    }
058
059    public int getSize() {
060      return size;
061    }
062
063    public void setSize(int size) {
064      this.size = size;
065    }
066
067    public int getGuessCount() {
068      return guessCount;
069    }
070
071    public void setGuessCount(int guessCount) {
072      this.guessCount = guessCount;
073    }
074
075    @NonNull
076    public Duration getDuration() {
077      return duration;
078    }
079
080    public void setDuration(@NonNull Duration duration) {
081      this.duration = duration;
082    }
083
084    public Long getUserId() {
085      return userId;
086    }
087
088    public void setUserId(Long userId) {
089      this.userId = userId;
090    }
091  }
